Ning, makinig ka.

00:13:30.400 --> 00:13:31.800
May bagong natuklasan.

00:13:32.880 --> 00:13:34.200
Ang puso ng ikatlong biktima

00:13:34.200 --> 00:13:36.600
nagkaroon ng coronary intervention surgery

00:13:36.800 --> 00:13:37.360
sa aming lugar.

00:13:37.360 --> 00:13:39.920
Tanging ang City Central Hospital lamang ang maaaring magsagawa ng operasyong ito.

00:13:39.920 --> 00:13:40.760
Okay, nakuha ko.

00:13:41.320 --> 00:13:42.920
Punta tayo sa City Central Hospital.

00:13:42.920 --> 00:13:43.250
Okay.

